description:
Sonic and Bartleby have dinner with Bartleby's parents in an effort to prove to the Montclair family that Sonic worthy of taking on the Montclair name when the time comes...
Don't forget to like, comment and subscribe! Also consider joining me on patreon to support my art!
https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
